{"id": 419, "genre": 1001, "title": "你最见不得哪些公主病症状？", "description": "因娇生惯养导致的自恋型人格障碍。少女，药不能停！（长得好看的除外）", "record_count": 6247, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183724ci68XJegaIwr4vqo.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-07-09T12:35:10Z", "options": [{"id": 3318, "content": "诶呦 嗯～～    不要啦～  了啦～  各种耍贱    心机婊  不行啦 我减肥  ～ 这个吃完还请吃烧烤吧～  ", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138993}, {"id": 3321, "content": "人丑多作怪", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130521}, {"id": 3246, "content": "王子病", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3247, "content": "出门我给拎包。本人女。", "image": null, "praise_count": 67, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114367}, {"id": 3248, "content": "公主病，穷人命", "image": null, "praise_count": 156, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3328, "content": "自拍狂魔", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138933}, {"id": 3331, "content": "整天一副自命不凡的样子，高傲", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138451}, {"id": 3259, "content": "我平时/我在家/我从来/我才不/我不要 这类的  ", "image": null, "praise_count": 157, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3260, "content": "什么都要别人伺候还理所当然", "image": null, "praise_count": 176, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138397}, {"id": 3254, "content": "我好生气，我要打你", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 135145}, {"id": 3262, "content": "出门前化妆超过一个小时，为等她，我天天吃早午饭。", "image": null, "praise_count": 69, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136898}, {"id": 3267, "content": "包太沉，帮我拎", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234821gTPNclo8uKrRhFwC.jpg", "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 99956}, {"id": 3270, "content": "我就是任性咋了？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137944}, {"id": 3271, "content": "看许晴", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 108470}, {"id": 3268, "content": "任何事任何话题都觉得在映射她。", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136076}, {"id": 3264, "content": "和闺蜜出去狂发照片，还只美颜自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 70, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138467}, {"id": 3269, "content": "打扮怪异，行为诡异。", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 133412}, {"id": 4280, "content": "并不是公主毛病比公主还多", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145732}, {"id": 3875, "content": "明明很无理的要求，还要装无辜的问“ 为什么不可以 ”！无辜你妹啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138802}, {"id": 3877, "content": "喜欢吃一家餐厅的非重点。\r\n“我喜欢吃这家餐厅的那碗面上的那种葱。”", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234827XrnflvgJQ2jeUuIt.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114232}, {"id": 4361, "content": "屁事干不了，还TM老爱发脾气", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 101526}, {"id": 4485, "content": "所有人必须听她的围着她转。不把别人放在眼里", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146749}, {"id": 5556, "content": "快点，帮我提包！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 148093}, {"id": 5507, "content": "然而讨厌他们并没有什么卵用，世界上就是有这么一群人消耗着你的耐心，你还不能neng死她", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147945}, {"id": 6097, "content": "长得一脸矫情的公主病", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149663}, {"id": 7427, "content": "你敢骂我？我叫我哥哥打你！【让我笑会儿】", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155952}, {"id": 3336, "content": "我不能吃。。。\n我不能看。。。\n我不能做。。。\n最受不了", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 38139}, {"id": 3597, "content": "人丑多八卦", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 90928}, {"id": 4110, "content": "装逼，说话嗲嗲的，超恶心，莫名其妙发脾气!", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234832dbXmuTJny5B4VDC1.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144685}, {"id": 4111, "content": "装逼，说话嗲嗲的，超恶心，莫名其妙发脾气!", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234832DHAT9oieYRGPwh2Z.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144685}, {"id": 3346, "content": "哎呀，这个事儿我不管了，你看着办吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 87684}, {"id": 3349, "content": "小姐心，丫鬟命。", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137032}, {"id": 3353, "content": "虽然我长得不行条件不行，但是我的另一半必须高富帅", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211146MnlQKu0Y8FoptSGh.jpg", "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115714}, {"id": 7705, "content": "长得不咋地，认为自己很牛逼，谁都得围着转，不转都不行。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 158342}, {"id": 3356, "content": "整天黑着个脸，在那里装高冷", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139358}, {"id": 3368, "content": "想说的都被说了", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138687}, {"id": 3370, "content": "娇生惯养的", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139497}, {"id": 3375, "content": "又装，又作，毛病多，还以为自己多可爱…", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 132859}, {"id": 3376, "content": "一天到晚觉得别人为她做事都是应该的，不帮她做事还抱怨……浑然不觉周围的人有多怨念", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3378, "content": "我交代你这么几个简单的事都办不到，不就占用你点时间么？不就花你几个钱么？真是小气鬼(操，关键我踏马也不是你对象，我踏马也是个女的啊)", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115714}, {"id": 3384, "content": "BB事，事事B", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139722}, {"id": 27704, "content": "我抽烟、纹身、乱性、自私、不懂事儿……但我是个好姑娘，你眼没瞎就该爱我…………我去你妈的！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 319049}, {"id": 3390, "content": "\"你这人怎么这样啊？就只是叫你帮个忙而已\"", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 133773}, {"id": 3660, "content": "觉得", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141997}, {"id": 3661, "content": "就她最牛逼，一切看她心情来。不好意思看不惯  请你自己走。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141997}, {"id": 3408, "content": "把没礼貌当真性情", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 140029}, {"id": 3409, "content": "进各种餐厅，迂回全场挑座位，刚坐下开始抱怨空调灯光气味…", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 140036}, {"id": 3410, "content": "我跟你说 就是那个什么什么 全世界只有她最懂 我们都是土鳖?", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 132942}, {"id": 6490, "content": "总是麻烦别人，性格不讨喜", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147548}, {"id": 3423, "content": "心比天高命比纸薄。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 105282}]}